    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The body shows extensive rust on the wheel arches and undercarriage, and the paint has severe oxidation and peeling. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a noticeable knock, and the transmission shifts harshly. The interior is heavily worn with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics, making this an ideal candidate for a dedicated restorer or for use as a parts donor.",
