    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hi there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for its next owner! Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to go and has been super reliable for me. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a great new home. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat and show you around the car!",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a recently inspected subframe and refreshed bushings. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual and a variable M-differential lock. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals are robust\u2014VANOS has been serviced, and the rod bearings are within spec. It\u2019s a driver-focused machine with a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline, offering the visceral feedback and balanced weight distribution enthusiasts demand.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Clean title. Reliable engine. Recent service history available. Minor exterior scratches. Interior well-maintained.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan offers a premium driving experience and remains in solid mechanical and cosmetic shape. The exterior is finished in a timeless Metallic Silver that retains a high-gloss luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear passenger door. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and features supple black leather seating; the upholstery is free of rips or tears, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster consistent with careful use. All electronic features, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and premium sound system, function perfectly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises, backed by a complete service history and a recent oil change. The tires are matching Continentals with plenty of tread depth remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This car has been garage-kept and primarily used for highway commuting, ensuring it remains a reliable and sharp-looking vehicle for its next owner.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection, ensuring reliable performance and a refined driving experience. Featuring a clean interior and a well-preserved exterior finish, it represents a premier opportunity for the sophisticated buyer seeking dependable transportation at a competitive market value. We invite you to experience the caliber of this exceptional offering firsthand.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-cared for over the years. It's the perfect fit for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road and handles like a dream. I've loved every mile in it, and I'm sure you will too! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 equipped with the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six and a 6-speed manual transmission. This example features precise throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and a robust power band aided by double-VANOS timing. The chassis is well-sorted, featuring a factory M-variable differential lock and recent subframe reinforcement for enhanced torsional rigidity. Maintenance is up-to-date, including a cooling system refresh and valve adjustment. While it exhibits minor cosmetic wear commensurate with its age, the mechanical vitals remain strong, providing a visceral, analog driving experience on staggered Style 67 alloys.",
